April you might be interested in researching some others who are/were involved in EVP-ITC communication. Marcello Bacci, Hans Otto Koenig, George Meek, Ernst Senkowski, Adolph Holmes, Sonia Rinaldi, just to name a few. Researchers across the world explore this in great detail.

Many experiments are done with that idea in mind such as the spiricom experiemnts past and present, direct voice communications, Frank&#39;s box, and various other methods.

Frank R just pointed out a great video that was posted interviewing Dr. Ernst Senkowski in which he gives an interesting viewpoint and some what he says mirrors my own point of view as well as info being given via EVP on many topics. He also speaks about some of the various researchers he knew.

http://vimeo.com/5637666

There is so much going on in the world that most people in the USA have very little knowledge of simply because they do not speak the language that the info is being presented in. There are some videos of other researchers on the web as well and if you can get past the language differences you may find some of their work to be very fascinating.

Misty


